# simple-crud-employee-manager 📝

This project was made just for practice - mainly to get hands-of experience with building a simple backend API, and then connecting it to a basic frontend that can interact with it.

## What this is about

- Practice building a RESTful API (CRUD) using basic tools like Node.js and Express
- Practice connecting a frontend to a custom API
- Learn how frontend and backedn can commnuicate with each other in a simple way

## Tech Stack

- **Backend:** Node.js + Express
- **Frontend:** Vite, React, tailwindcss
- **Database:** Just using a local JSON file

## 📦 Installation & Setup

### 1. Clone this repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/vong0-0/simple-crud-employee-manager.git
cd simple-crud-employee-manager
```

### 2. Install dependencies

#### 🔧 Backend

```bash
cd server
npm install
```

#### 💻 Frontend

```bash
cd ../frontend
npm install
```

## 🚀 Running the Project

Open two terminals to run the backend and frontend separately.

### ▶️ Start the Backend Server

```bash
cd server
npm run start
```

### 💡 Start the Frontend Development Server

```bash
cd frontend
npm run dev
```
